title: Kiss Person Man Medium Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic kiss between a man and another person, with the man's skin tone depicted as medium-dark. It signifies affection, love, and intimacy.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts two men sharing a gentle kiss, with the left figure sporting a medium skin tone and the right a dark skin tone.  Their faces are softly rounded, with subtle blushes and closed eyes conveying affection and tenderness.  Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and realistic lighting create a warm, intimate portrayal of romantic connection.
